text: "Taco Grande" is a song by "Weird Al" Yankovic. It is a parody of Gerardo's song "Rico Suave". It is about the singer wanting Mexican food and his visit to a fake Mexican restaurant. It was released in the 1992 album Off the Deep End. Category:"Weird Al" Yankovic songs Category:Parodies Category:1992 songs
title: Taco Grande
